snippet.textDisplay: Djokovic's medical exemptions were given by the State Government Health to play in the AO., That is all. I also read a report which stated that the two State Government Health''s exemptions were wrktten on 'Tennis Australia's' letter head. However the permission to enter Australia (Cross Border) is the Federal Government's responsibility. Applying for a e-visa overseas to enter Australia and getting approved does not automatically gain you entrance at the border. You still have to undergo an interviewed by Border Force to verify your credentials and intention to enter Australia. There have been many many cases where individuals arriving on tourist e-visas and fail to convince authorities of their genuine intentions have had their visas cancelled and put back on the next plane. Djokovic's well publicised stance on vaccinations got him undone today. He is only to blame not his travel agent as he claims.
